msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Fa o tswa mo US, re akelang NOWPayments (mafelo a mafe, go fetlewa go mo "
"wallet ya gago). Fa o mo US, Stripe Crypto gape ke keletso. O ka eba le "
"ditshebeletso tse ngata le go fa baeng ba gago go khetha!"

msgid "Enabled Payment Methods"
msgstr "Dikakanyo tsa Thuto di Efaegileng"

msgid ""
"Select which payment options will appear in your widget. Your visitors can "
"choose their preferred method."
msgstr ""
"Kgetha ditshebeletso tsa thuto tse tla bonala mo widget ya gago. Baeng ba "
"gago ba ka kgetha tsela ya bone ya go rata."

