"Display your wallet address so users can send crypto directly. Zero fees, "
"but requires users to already have crypto."
msgstr ""
"Bontsha morero wa wallet ya gago gore modirisi a tsegelo a go romela crypto "
"ka mo go sepe. Mafelo a sa se leng, empa a golisa gore ba le crypto go "
"lekola."

