"crypto wallet. Funds go straight to your wallet – no middleman."
msgstr ""
"NOWPayments e o di tla go amogela diipayiseng tsa mokgatlo ka tsela ya "
"direlo ya gago. Dithuto di tsena go direga – ga go na ngwala wa godimo."

