msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Ditšebelisano tsa Stripe Crypto (USDC) di akaretse fela mo dipeseteng tsa "
"US. Fa o seka mo US, Stripe e tla amogela fela ditšebelisano tsa karideo go "
"bala ya gago ya Stripe (go se dire ka go crypto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Fa o na mo US, o ka dirisa Stripe go amogela crypto ka mo go se. Fa o seka "
"mo US, o swane le NOWPayments kgotsa CoinGate go amogela crypto ka mo go se."

