msgstr "Bohlale Gopolo Gwe Gase re re"

msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Moeng wa kgolo, wo sekgolo wa kgontshano le tsholo e e lokelang go tshegetsa"
" ba ba rego ka khadra ya dikadiri goba crypto (Quai). Ga go na difees tsa "
"selemo, ga go na ditshono tsa thibelo ya boroko – mo wallet ya gago le "
"ditsebi tsa sekgolo."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Mothapo e e nngwe e dirisa dipalo tsa thibelo. Proxy e e dirisa dipalo mo "
"serwereng sa gago go tsena go go fosa dipalo."

msgid ""
"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"O ka ntšha diphetho tsa script fa tlase fa diphetho tsa ntlha di fetoha goba"
" fa o batla go dirisa CDN e e sa le ya sengwe."

